) 9: Sample c′ uniformly from C(q) \ {c}
10: // following three updates are done simultaneously 11: uw ← uw − η · rw,c · ρ′(ξ−1w,c) · `′ (〈uw,vc − vc′〉) · (vc − vc′) 12: vc ← vc − η · rw,c · ρ′(ξ−1w,c) · `′ (〈uw,vc − vc′〉) · uw 13: vc′ ← vc′ + η · rw,c · ρ′(ξ−1w,c) · `′ (〈uw,vc − vc′〉) · uw 14: until predefined time limit is exceeded 15: end for 16: // Stage 2: Update Ξ in parallel for all machine q ∈ {1, 2, . . . , p} do in parallel 17: Fetch all vc ∈ V 18: for w ∈ W(q) do 19: for c ∈ C do 20: ξw,c = α/ (∑ c′∈C\{c} ` (〈uw,vc − vc′〉) + β
